Rodimus's signal gets Jackie pointed in the right direction.  "Sorry 
about the wait," he says as he tromps in with Blackfang draped in his 
arms like a rug on display.  "I got lost in the corridors.  Never 
been here before, y'know?"  He would have smiled if his mouth wasn't 
covered by an unmoving faceplate.
